Hi Daniel

I hope you are well!

I have reviewed your request 00435845 – Migrate Netwrix Auditor to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor.
I am writing to arrange a meeting to discuss your options with Professional Services.
I've included our Account Manager: Marti Watt and Enterprise Solutions Manager: Scott Forsyth in this email to help coordinate the details.

Here are the key points we would like to cover during the meeting:
Professional Services:

  *   Planning: Our Service team will assist in creating a comprehensive plan tailored to your specific requirements.
  *   Installation and Configuration: They will guide us through the entire installation and configuration process, ensuring everything is set up correctly and efficiently.

Scope for Use Case:

  *   Defining Requirements: The services team will work with us to define the scope of our use case, ensuring that all our specific needs and requirements are met.
  *   Customization: They will help identify any necessary customizations to optimize the upgrade for our particular use case.
  *   Implementation Support: Ongoing support during the implementation phase to address any issues or adjustments needed.

Please note that these services are part of our Professional Service offerings and may incur additional charges.
Let us know your availability for the meeting, and if there were any additional points you would like to discuss.


Thank you
Alex Buchta
Technical Support Manager
